Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.08,0:01:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类因人口膨胀而向宇宙移民已过了半个世纪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.23,0:01:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球周围漂浮着巨大的人工都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.77,0:01:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为人类的“第二故乡”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.86,0:01:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们就在这里出生、成长、生儿育女\N并走向死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.82,0:01:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙世纪0079年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.83,0:02:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离地球最远的宇宙都市SIDE 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.31,0:02:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以ZION公国之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.46,0:02:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向地球联邦政府发起了独立战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.16,0:02:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在开始一个月的战斗里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.77,0:02:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION公国和地球联邦军有半数以上的人口死去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.84,0:02:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们对于自己的行为产生了恐惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.90,0:02:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战争由此进入胶着状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.64,0:02:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,历时八个多月……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.53,0:02:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‘GUNDAM挺立大地！！’
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.83,0:03:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史立达，你留在这里等我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.30,0:03:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，曹长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.33,0:04:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曹长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.25,0:04:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,军事设施似在右面建筑物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在是上班时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.83,0:04:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但只见一部车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.88,0:04:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连一个人也看不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.61,0:04:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.15,0:04:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看见了，是个小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.18,0:04:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.48,0:04:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.89,0:04:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.69,0:04:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早餐还未吃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.07,0:04:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.40,0:04:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我早知会是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.93,0:04:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不吃早餐会饿坏身体的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.70,0:04:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈罗，阿姆罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.80,0:04:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈罗，阿姆罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.14,0:04:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈罗你看来很精神呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.04,0:04:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Thank you，阿姆罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.98,0:04:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗，你准备穿什么出去？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.38,0:05:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.85,0:05:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待我修理好计算机之后便会去吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.42,0:05:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道你没有听到避难命令吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.45,0:05:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,避难命令？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.49,0:05:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才那警号吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.16,0:05:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真气人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.73,0:05:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没听到军方广播吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.69,0:05:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,军舰入港所以要到避难所啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.86,0:05:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.46,0:05:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不知道啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.71,0:05:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗！没时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.80,0:05:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.20,0:05:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请各位快到避难所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.80,0:05:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在对面等你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.77,0:05:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈罗 跟我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是啰唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.08,0:05:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.58,0:05:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.20,0:05:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙劳·波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.62,0:05:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎可以这样？是邻居啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.75,0:05:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么不通知阿姆罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.45,0:05:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说避难的事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.39,0:05:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊！只有他一人仍留在家里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.29,0:05:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但...如果没阿姆罗爸爸的军方技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.13,0:05:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们又怎会...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.53,0:05:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们是因为要建设研究基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.00,0:05:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才要大家搬，你还生气吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.97,0:05:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是这个意思...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.04,0:05:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.23,0:05:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.80,0:05:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.18,0:06:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗！真没礼貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.35,0:06:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你爸爸是否在将入港的军舰上？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.25,0:06:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.09,0:06:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一星期前说会从地球回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.66,0:06:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里会成为战场吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.93,0:06:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸什么也没跟我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.97,0:06:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,将White Base的零件尽快搬到母舰上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.88,0:06:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫技工们快手一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.65,0:06:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真想不到White Base会被ZION跟踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦？这个就是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.58,0:06:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.39,0:06:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是我们联邦军的新锐母舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.66,0:06:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这舰和GUNDAM完成的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.13,0:06:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们要打败ZION国便轻而易举
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.48,0:07:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,报告，我们已到达SIDE 7
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.25,0:07:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请尽快到舰桥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.79,0:07:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.42,0:07:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的名字是布莱特？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.20,0:07:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.63,0:07:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你加入军队有多久？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.16,0:07:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,六个月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.53,0:07:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十九岁吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.20,0:07:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.50,0:07:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到GUNDAM可以量产时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.90,0:07:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们这些少年就不用上战场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.84,0:07:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到时战争也都结束了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.84,0:07:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是你的儿子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.58,0:07:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的，听说你们这年纪的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.61,0:07:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都要加入游击队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.21,0:07:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.95,0:07:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，据说是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.45,0:07:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你了，雷上尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.19,0:07:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这母舰终也逃不出敌人的追踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.16,0:08:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是遗憾...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.28,0:08:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来我的运气真坏...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.08,0:08:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然在作战完毕回航途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.05,0:08:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遇上这件猎物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.32,0:08:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又或者是他们的运气好吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.79,0:08:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，夏亚少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.46,0:08:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是在这偏僻的卫星内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.63,0:08:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会有联邦军的V作战计划？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.93,0:08:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.56,0:08:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能他们在开发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.57,0:08:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比我们的ZAKU更优秀的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.34,0:08:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会吧！这偏僻的卫星...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还没有消息回来吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.74,0:08:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.44,0:08:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暗号是C.C.2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.15,0:08:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看！我的预测证实了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.41,0:08:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那即是说联邦已有机动战士？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.79,0:09:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该说是开发并且己成功了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.12,0:09:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三台也是机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.03,0:09:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来里面还有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.66,0:09:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在是攻击的最好时机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.66,0:09:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的任务只在于侦察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.27,0:09:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但被他们装上战舰之后便...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.14,0:09:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必急于争功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.61,0:09:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,占！你想干什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.14,0:09:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亚少校不也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.75,0:09:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打胜了仗才升官的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.12,0:09:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,占！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.42,0:09:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想违抗命令？快停手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.96,0:09:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要我立了大功便可出人头地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.24,0:10:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要打败敌人是越快动手越好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.99,0:10:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在附近的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.90,0:10:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种震动的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.03,0:10:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.64,0:10:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.84,0:10:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是ZION军的攻击！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.57,0:10:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.78,0:10:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去找爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.91,0:10:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.18,0:10:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你出去会为我们添麻烦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.28,0:10:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我爸是军人，这里不能持久的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.98,0:10:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去看看能否到军舰里避难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.95,0:10:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.36,0:10:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.17,0:10:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.26,0:10:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请关上门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.80,0:10:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION国的机动战士！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.97,0:10:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是ZION国的ZAKU
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.48,0:11:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！平民要去避难的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.58,0:11:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要找雷总技师\N你知他在那里
